{"tid":967070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎汶洛擬戰區選　劍指安達選區　黎：不放棄九東工作","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T02:28:56.000Z","uid":145488,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d19fc183902c84f66873688f166765844c907261","tid":967070,"uid":145488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"已退出香港眾志的黎汶洛近期再度活躍於政壇，繼早前出戰社工註冊局選舉後，據了解，黎汶洛擬參選2019年區議會選舉，落戶觀塘安達新選區。<br />\n<br />\n黎汶洛接受《香港01》查詢時表示，不會就區議會選舉部署作出回應，不過強調已在該區展開地區工作，並正與當區民主派協調。他表示，他於2016年立法會選舉棄選時，已表明不會放棄九龍東的地區工作，如今「落區」是兌現當時的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/278107/%E6%94%BF%E5%9C%88%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2-%E9%BB%8E%E6%B1%B6%E6%B4%9B%E6%93%AC%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8-%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%89%E9%81%94%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%80-%E9%BB%8E-%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E4%B9%9D%E6%9D%B1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F278107%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%259C%2588%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%25B1%25B6%25E6%25B4%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E5%258A%258D%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%258D%2580-%25E9%25BB%258E-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUXwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e33401de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/278107/%E6%94%BF%E5%9C%88%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2-%E9%BB%8E%E6%B1%B6%E6%B4%9B%E6%93%AC%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8-%E5%8A%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%89%E9%81%94%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%80-%E9%BB%8E-%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E4%B9%9D%E6%9D%B1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C</a>"},{"pid":"6355978f6c92c9354061ff52f5e1c8778f8d03fd","tid":967070,"uid":145488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" cl